          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "The ambient weather around a peng is always lightly cloudy with a pleasant breeze, and the temperature is pleasantly warm for the season. Another creature that attempts to alter the weather within this aura; otherwise, the effect is disrupted. The peng can activate or deactivate this aura as a single action with the concentrate trait.",
